name: Water Skeeters 2
description: Growing up near rivers in central Texas, some of my most formative thoughts happened in moments staring deep into the space where undulating water met cypress-filled banks. Because of this, I've always had a soft spot for water skeeters/skippers, the bugs that skip on the surface of the water. This series pays homage to this special and strange time in Texas & the role that local flora & fauna play in our lives.
